Privacy Policy for Tough Life

We, 'Crunchy' , respect the privacy of our users and are committed to protecting their personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard information collected through our game "Tough Life" available on the Google Play Store.

Information We Collect

Tough Life is a simple game designed for entertainment purposes. We do not collect any personally identifiable information from users of the game, nor do we collect any information about their devices.

Third-Party Services

Tough Life may have integrated with Google Analytics, a third-party analytics service provided by Google, to gather anonymous usage data for the purpose of improving the game and user experience. Google Analytics may collect information such as device type, operating system, and usage statistics in accordance with Google's privacy policy.

Data Security

Tough Life does not collect any user data, including personal information or device data. Therefore, there is no data stored or transmitted through the game, and no measures are needed to protect such data.

Children's Privacy

Tough Life is suitable for users of all ages and does not contain content intended for children under the age of 13. While the game is family-friendly and does not collect personal information from users, we encourage parents and guardians to monitor their children's use of digital devices and online activities. If you believe that your child has provided us with personal information without your consent, please contact us immediately so that we can take appropriate action.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update or change our Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the revised Privacy Policy on this page. We encourage users to periodically review this Privacy Policy for any updates.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or the privacy practices related to Tough Life, please contact us at divyarajraol007@outlook.com
